removeWeapon 
Behavior: local 
Game: Operation Flashpoint (1.00) 
Description: Remove weapon from a unit.  
Note: It is possible to create invalid combinations with this command 
 (ie, attempting to remove a weapon that a unit does not possess 
). When doing so, application behaviour is undefined.  
Syntax:  
 unitName removeWeapon weaponName 
Parameters: 
unitName: Object 
weaponName: String 
Return Value: 
 Nothing